ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend the course to another student because of Professor Allen. He is such a great presence. I would warn though to be ready to be flexible in terms of how the course goes and the different expectations from week to week.
WGSS 900 is a workshop that will force you to reflect on your commitment to studies of WGSS, how your work contributes to the field, and how to approach teaching it.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course was very helpful to me and the research I want to do. It did the most for me in terms of thinking about my intellectual identity and the way I want to approach my work. It also helped me work through my own project as a feminist project and get me started thinking about my prospectus and methodology.
